#: ../../S/sysape.rst:9
msgid ""
"A rather derogatory term for a computer operator; a play on :ref:`sysop` "
"common at sites that use the banana hierarchy of problem complexity (see "
":ref:`one-banana-problem`\\)."
msgstr ""
"コンピュータのオペレータを指す、かなり軽蔑的な用語。\\ :ref:`sysop`\\ をもじったもので、問題の複雑さのbananaの階層(\\ "
":ref:`one-banana-problem`\\ を参照)を使うサイトで一般的だ。"
